== Installation =

include_once("$IP/extensions/gadgets/Gadgets.php");

== Configuration ==

$wgGadgetsAllowed = array();
$wgGadgetsAllowed['end_of_days'] = 'Their <blink>tags</blink> shall <blink>blink</blink> until the end of days.';

== Use on the wiki ==

Now, on a wiki page, you can write:

{{#gadget: end_of_days}}

and get back the raw HTML message above.
